‘Dine with Designers’ Kindles Zeal Amongst the Designers in Hisar


Hisar [India], December 2: Building Material Reporter (BMR) conducted the 'Dine with Designers’ at Hisar, prepping up for the much awaited gala event, Smartex 2024 New Delhi Edition.


The event took place on December 2, 2023, at the Lemon Tree Hotel Hisar, marking the celebration and success of hard work by the designers and architects of the region.  This event marks the fourth edition of the gala symposium in the field of design and architecture.

 

 

The event was a huge success marking the presence of many distinguished architects and designers including the key industry stakeholders. The brands that showed their presence were VOX Building Products India Pvt. Ltd., Benchmark Lifestyle Solutions (Qualita), Ventura International Pvt. Ltd., Gujarat Guardian Limited, Purbanchal Laminates Pvt. Ltd. (Amulya Mica), Haryana Doors, Vibrant Technik, Kerakoll India Pvt. Ltd. and Home Decor. 

 

Read More: PM Modi All Set to Inaugurate Biggest Office in the World on December 17 in Surat

 

Objective

 

Within the domains of architecture and design, this event acted as a focal point for cooperation, creativity, and inspiration. Leading regional architects, designers, and consultants joined forces with top national and international brands at the event.

 

The industry is buzzing about Dine with Designers' success, which further demonstrates our dedication to encouraging cooperation, creativity, and inspiration in the field of architecture and design. With the motive to ignite the essence of encouragement in the Tier 2 and Tier 3 cities, our last event in Guwahati also thoroughly celebrated the designers with lauds and praises. 

 

Read More: Ayodhya’s Ram Mandir Is All Getting Set to Be Open for the Pilgrims

 

Highlights


 

The team Smartex presented Lifetime achievement Award to Ar. Satish Kumar Singla, for his phenomenal contribution in the architectural and design world. Apart from working as a Professor & Architect Advisor in former reputed platforms, his works have set grounds of motivation in the field of design. 

 

The awardee list also included exponential work of the individuals form the city. Some of the recipients of the honour were  Ar. Sunny Garg and Ar.  Ekta Garg, Ar. Ankit Gera, Ar. Ajayender Beniwal, Dipesh & Uma, Ar. Pankaj Garhwal, Ar. Akshat Mehta and Ar. Paramvir Kumar. Also, the Smartex Prime Award went to  Ar. Nitin Kumar and Ar. Shilpa Kumar of RS Architects for their unbeatable contribution in the field of design. 

 

Read More: The Change in the Construction & Design Industry- It’s Getting Better

 

Future Endeavors


Dine with Designers: Chapter Hisar posed to be a huge success, encouraging us to organise more such events in future. Building Material Reporter is a prominent platform that honors and recognizes exceptional work produced by individuals in a variety of industries. We are having the mega Smartex event in February 2024 with lots of interactions and celebrations ahead. The brand aims to empower, inspire, and connect professionals, is essential to promoting development, creativity, and teamwork. 


BMR continues to bring together professionals, enthusiasts, and leaders in the architecture and design industry in India to collaborate, learn, and inspire, with a primary focus on creating networking opportunities.
